Package: fars
Title: Summarize and plot US traffic fatalities 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Adi", "Gherman", email = "adig@jhu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package is using the US National Highway Traffic Safety Administration's Fatality Analysis Reporting System census data to provide a yearly summary as well as plotting traffic accident fatalities in the US for each state.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.1)
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
  dplyr, tidyr, maps, graphics, magrittr, readr
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown,
    testthat
VignetteBuilder: knitr
